org.geotools.gpx2.gpxentities
Interface Track

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicTrack
public interface Track

Represents a GPX track. A track is made up of a TrackSegments. Each TrackSegment in a Track object contains SimpleWaypoints that represent the "track points" in the Track.

See Also:
TrackSegment, SimpleWaypoint, BasicTrack, BasicTrackSegment
